\c 54
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukusizwa ezitheni
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Ngamachacho. Masikili. EsikaDavida. Lapho amaZifi eza athi kuSawuli: UDavida kacatshanga yini kithi?
\p
\v 1 Nkulunkulu, ngisindisa ngebizo lakho, ungahlulele ngamandla akho.
\v 2 Nkulunkulu, zwana umkhuleko wami, ubeke indlebe emazwini omlomo wami\x + Hlab. 55.1.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba abemzini bangivukele, abalolunya badinga umphefumulo wami, kababekanga uNkulunkulu phambi kwabo. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 18.44,45. 144.7. Hlab. 86.14.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Khangela, uNkulunkulu ungumsizi wami\x + Hlab. 118.7.\x*; iNkosi ilalabo abasekela umphefumulo wami\x + Hlab. 118.7.\x*.
\v 5 Izaphindisela ububi ezitheni zami. Baqume\x + Hlab. 143.12.\x* ngeqiniso lakho\x + Hlab. 89.49.\x*.
\v 6 Ngizanikela umhlatshelo kuwe ngokukhululeka\x + Nani 15.3. Hlab. 51.12. Hos. 14.4.\x*, ngizadumisa ibizo lakho, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba lihle\x + Hlab. 52.9.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba ungikhulule ekuhluphekeni konke, lelihlo lami libonile \add isiloyiso sami\add* ezitheni zami\x + Hlab. 59.10. 92.11. 112.8. 118.7.\x*.
